{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A short, cinematic western shooter with wild, fast-paced spray 'n' pray action! Help a sharp-shootin' renegade on a mission to take over the saloon. Shoot first, ask questions never. Clear out anyone daring enough to stand in your way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A brutal showdown awaits. It\u2019s you against the entire town!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313230/extras/Gangs.png?t=1734456756\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle through four ruthless gangs that control the saloon and claim your place as the ultimate gunslinger. Only one can come out on top. Get ready for the fight of your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Origins of the Saloon King</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game was originally submitted to Jern Jam 3. I was so happy with the result, plus it won an award for <i>Cinematography &amp; Completeness</i>\u00a0that I decided to expand and improve it. I'm excited to share the updated version on Steam as a freebie!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Snacking on the Rattles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3313230/1dfeff2831ae8f593c773d0c5b66009dbb5a675d.jpg"},{"name":"The Three Bodyteers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3313230/686c5c6a941f4939ab3121c3a102887bde60ea50.jpg"},{"name":"Stop the Union","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3313230/385f425f3834e30851e9c33936c78d6e4fcbe144.jpg"},{"name":"The Saloon King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3313230/e37d56da43f3c36db3a6e7cfefb79471563af842.jpg"},{"name":"No Innocents in This Town","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/st